<h1><span id="Steinitz_Deferred">Steinitz Deferred</span></h1>
<p>This move is a good developing move for black. It re-enforces the e-pawn, it allows the c8 bishop to readily join the battle and reserves the option of an f5 push. It does, however, impede the progress of the f8 bishop. This move is much more popular than the true Steinitz Defence.
</p>
